    <label>VanDrelarh</label>
    <description>The VanDrelarh are remnants of a forgotten experiment, abducted wanderers reshaped in a forsaken laboratory that sought to forge the ultimate predators. Blending feral strength with fragments of ancient knowledge, these creatures are incomplete—beasts caught between what they were and what they were meant to become. When the lab fell to unknown forces, only a few escaped into the world. Time twists them: some fight to keep their humanity, while others yield to the beast inside, becoming relentless hunters under the broken moon.</description>
    <descriptionShort>Half-made children of a forsaken experiment, the VanDrelarh wander as fractured predators—part human, part beast, bearing forbidden knowledge and the curse of eventual transformation.</descriptionShort>
    <iconPath>UI/Icons/Xenotypes/Custom/Yttakin_8</iconPath>
    <inheritable>true</inheritable>
